(8, 'full-stack-development ', 'website-development', '{\n    \"title\": \"Full Stack Web Development Services\",\n    \"section2\": {\n      \"title\": \"Build Reliable Digital Solutions With Confidence\",\n      \"des\": \"Choosing to hire full stack developers can feel overwhelming. Many businesses worry about hiring the wrong talent, wasting money on freelancers, or ending up with code that doesn’t scale. At Allspark Technologies, we remove those worries. Our dedicated full stack developers deliver complete web development solutions covering both front end and back end web development, so your website or application runs smoothly, securely, and grows with your business. Whether you need a freelance full stack developer for a short project or a long-term full stack developer hire, we ensure reliable delivery every time.\"\n    },\n    \"section3\": {\n      \"title\": \"Full Stack Web Development Services We Offer\",\n      \"image\": \"img1.png\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Development Without Gaps\",\n          \"description\": \"A common concern is that separate teams for front end and back end web development may create miscommunication and errors. With Allspark, you hire full stack developers who handle everything end to end. Our services include front end web development services, back end web development, API integration, database design, and full stack web development services for scalable applications.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Clear Hiring Options Without Surprises\",\n          \"description\": \"Many worry about unclear costs or the risks of freelance full stack developers. At Allspark, you can choose flexible models, hire full stack developers full-time, part-time, or remote based on your project needs. As a transparent partner, we ensure predictable pricing with no hidden fees.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Visibility That Attracts Users\",\n          \"description\": \"One major fear is that a web application won’t attract the right audience. Every solution we deliver includes SEO-friendly full stack web development services, helping your platform rank on search engines. Whether building a website or app, our developers ensure front end and back end web development is optimized for speed, search, and conversions.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Performance That Handles Growth\",\n          \"description\": \"Businesses often worry that poorly built apps will slow down or fail under high traffic. Our dedicated full stack developers build secure, scalable systems that keep performance steady, even when your business grows or demand spikes.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Easy Management & Updates\",\n          \"description\": \"Managing a new website can feel technical and overwhelming. Our full stack developer remote teams design user-friendly dashboards and provide post-launch support, so you can update content, manage users, and track performance easily.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Mobile-First Digital Experience\",\n          \"description\": \"More users access websites on their phones than desktops. Our full stack development team ensures responsive front end web development services and stable back end systems, so your application works seamlessly on all devices.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section4\": {\n      \"title\": \"Solutions That Scale With You\",\n      \"des\": \"Many clients fear that their digital platforms will struggle when integrations or customizations are needed. We provide full stack web development services with API development, secure payment integration, CRM and ERP connections, and cloud-ready deployments to ensure smooth scalability.\"\n    },\n    \"section5\": {\n      \"title\": \"How We Work\",\n      \"steps\": [\n        {\n          \"step\": 1,\n          \"title\": \"Discovery & Strategy\",\n          \"description\": \"We begin by learning