(11, 'api-integration-development', 'website-development', '{\n    \"title\": \"API Development and Integration Services\",\n    \"section2\": {\n      \"title\": \"Build Seamless Connections That Work\",\n      \"des\": \"Choosing an API development company can feel complex. Many businesses end up with integrations that are slow, unreliable, or hard to maintain. At Allspark Technologies, we deliver API development and integration services designed to simplify those concerns. Our developers build secure, scalable, and user-friendly APIs that connect applications, data, and workflows. Whether you need custom API development, payment gateway API integration, or enterprise-level REST API development services, we create solutions that keep your systems running smoothly.\"\n    },\n    \"section3\": {\n      \"title\": \"API Development Services We Offer\",\n      \"image\": \"img1.png\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Integration Without Barriers\",\n          \"description\": \"Many wonder how to develop APIs that connect with existing systems without breaking operations. As a trusted provider of API development services in the USA, we offer custom API development, REST API development services, SOAP API integration, and GraphQL API development. Just like leading technology companies rely on API integration to stay connected, we engineer APIs that simplify processes, reduce downtime, and improve communication between platforms.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Clear Pricing Without Surprises\",\n          \"description\": \"A frequent concern is hidden costs for integrations. At Allspark, our API integration services are offered with transparent, flexible pricing models. Whether you need a simple third-party connection or a custom enterprise API integration service, our packages are designed to grow alongside your business needs.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Performance That Delivers Results\",\n          \"description\": \"APIs are only valuable when they work quickly and reliably. Our API development service process includes optimization for performance, scalability, and security. From payment gateway API integration services to custom enterprise API integration services, we ensure your connections work smoothly across mobile, desktop, and cloud environments.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Security That Builds Confidence\",\n          \"description\": \"A major worry for businesses is whether their data will remain secure during and after integration. At Allspark, we build APIs with role-based access, encryption, and compliance standards. From REST API development services to payment gateway integrations, every connection is engineered to protect sensitive data while maintaining smooth operations.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section4\": {\n      \"title\": \"Why Businesses Struggle With APIs & How We Fix It\",\n      \"des\": \"Many companies delay investing in API integration services because they have seen integrations that break existing systems, are expensive, or take months to deploy. Others are unsure how to develop a reliable API that scales with their growing business. At Allspark, we solve these challenges by designing APIs that are simple, stable, and tailored to your exact business processes.\"\n    },\n    \"section5\": {\n      \"title\": \"How We Work\",\n      \"steps\": [\n        {\n          \"step\": 1,\n          \"title\": \"Discovery & Planning\",\n          \"description\": \"We begin by analyzing your current systems, workflows, and goals. As a leading API development company, our strategy is built around efficiency and long-term growth.\",\n          \"margin\": \"0px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 2,\n          \"title\": \"Custom Design & Development\",\n          \"description\": \"Our developers create tailored APIs designed to connect your applications with precision. From REST API development services to GraphQL API development, we focus on speed, usability, and scalability.\",\n          \"margin\": \"100px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 3,\n          \"title\": \"Integration & Optimization\",\n          \"description\": \"We integrate APIs with CRMs, ERPs, cloud platforms, and third-party tools. As part of our API integration services USA package, we also optimize for speed, security, and reliability.\",\n          \"margin\": \"200px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 4,\n          \"title\": \"Testing & Continuous Support\",\n          \"description\": \"Every custom API development project undergoes rigorous testing. Post-launch, we provide ongoing monitoring, updates, and technical support to ensure your systems remain connected without disruption.\",\n          \"margin\": \"300px\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section6\": {\n      \"image\": \"img2.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Build APIs That Drive Growth\",\n      \"des\": \"An API is more than just code, it is the backbone of smooth operations. As a trusted provider of API integration services in the USA, Allspark Technologies delivers secure, scalable, and high-performing solutions. From custom API development to payment gateway API integration, we build connections that fuel long-term business success.\",\n      \"des2\": \"Our expertise includes REST API development services, SOAP API integration, GraphQL API development, and custom enterprise API integration services. With Allspark, you do not just get APIs, you get a long-term partner focused on your growth. Businesses often ask if an API development company can guarantee security while enabling seamless integrations across multiple platforms. At Allspark, our solutions are secure by default, performance-driven, and built to grow with your operations.\"\n    },\n    \"section7\": {\n      \"quote\": \"Allspark handled our payment gateway API integration flawlessly. Transactions are now faster, and our reporting tools connect seamlessly across systems.\",\n      \"author\": \"Sarah T., Ecommerce Owner\"\n    },\n    \"section8\": {\n      \"image\": \"img3.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Why Choose Us\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Proven API Expertise\",\n          \"description\": \"We bring years of experience in custom API development, REST API development services, and enterprise integrations.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Secure and Scalable Solutions\",\n          \"description\": \"Our APIs are built to handle increasing loads while keeping data safe and compliant.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"User-Focused Development\",\n          \"description\": \"We design APIs that are easy to integrate and maintain, ensuring smooth use for developers and businesses alike.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Continuous Support & Optimization\",\n          \"description\": \"From bug fixes to new feature integrations, we ensure your APIs keep running at peak performance.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section9\": {\n      \"title\": \"Industries We Serve\",\n      \"para\": \"We have extensive experience providing API development and integration services across industries such as:\",\n      \"industries\": [\n        \"Healthcare & Pharma Platforms\",\n        \"Ecommerce & Payment Systems\",\n        \"B2B & Enterprise Solutions\",\n        \"Education & Learning Systems\",\n        \"Financial & Insurance Platforms\",\n        \"Technology & SaaS Integrations\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"faq\": {\n      \"title\": \"Frequently Asked Questions\",\n      \"faqs\": [\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-1\",\n          \"ques\": \"What are API development services?\",\n          \"ans\": \"API development services involve creating custom connections that allow applications and systems to share data and workflows securely.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-2\",\n          \"ques\": \"How much does custom API development cost?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Costs depend on complexity and integrations. As a leading API development company, we provide flexible packages to fit both startups and enterprises.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-3\",\n          \"ques\": \"Do you handle payment gateway API integration?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Yes. Our payment gateway API integration services ensure smooth transactions and secure data handling.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-4\",\n          \"ques\": \"How long does an API integration take?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Timelines vary. A simple integration may take 2–4 weeks, while large enterprise API integration services may take a few months.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-5\",\n          \"ques\": \"Can you update or replace old APIs?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Absolutely. We provide API migration, redesign, and optimization services to modernize outdated systems.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-6\",\n          \"ques\": \"Why partner with Allspark for API development?\",\n          \"ans\": \"We combine technical expertise, clear pricing, and long-term support, making us a reliable partner for API development and integration services.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"contact\": {\n      \"title\":\"Partner with Allspark Technologies today!\" ,\n      \"subTitle\":  \"Ready to simplify your systems with reliable API development and integration?\"\n    }\n}'),
(12, 'custom-web-app-development', 'website-development', '{\n    \"title\": \"Custom Web Application Development\",\n    \"section2\": {\n      \"title\": \"Build Web Apps That Perform\",\n      \"des\": \"Choosing a web application development company in the USA can be tough. Many web app development services result in platforms that are slow, insecure, or too complex for users. At Allspark Technologies, we deliver custom web application development that removes these challenges. Our web app developers build secure, scalable, and easy-to-use applications for businesses of every size. Whether you need enterprise web application development, eCommerce web application development, or healthcare web app development, we create solutions that help your business grow.\"\n    },\n    \"section3\": {\n      \"title\": \"Web Application Development Services We Offer\",\n      \"image\": \"img1.png\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Development Without Limits\",\n          \"description\": \"Many businesses wonder which is the best framework for web application development or which web application development platforms to choose. As a trusted custom web app development company, we guide you through every step. We provide enterprise web application development, progressive web app development services, healthcare solutions, and eCommerce platforms. Our team also works with AWS for advanced web application architecture for developing a dashboard for large dataset AWS solutions, ensuring speed and reliability.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Clear Pricing Without Surprises\",\n          \"description\": \"Many clients worry about costs when looking for web application development companies. At Allspark, our web application development service packages are transparent and flexible. Whether you want a simple custom app or a large-scale enterprise system, you get clear pricing designed to grow with your business.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Usability That Drives Adoption\",\n          \"description\": \"Some businesses have tried web and mobile application development companies only to end up with apps their teams never use. We focus on usability and user experience. From progressive web application development companies to java web application development company solutions, our applications are designed with responsive design, smooth navigation, and integrations that keep users engaged.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Security That Builds Confidence\",\n          \"description\": \"Secure web application development is critical when dealing with sensitive business and customer data. Our solutions use compliance-based standards, encryption, and role-based access. Whether in healthcare web app development, financial dashboards, or custom enterprise web application development, we ensure that your data stays safe.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section4\": {\n      \"title\": \"Why Businesses Struggle With Web Apps & How We Fix It\",\n      \"des\": \"Many companies avoid custom web app development because they’ve seen failed projects that were too costly, lacked scalability, or had poor adoption rates. Others do not know whether to hire web app developers or outsource to web application development companies. At Allspark, we address these issues with a proven process that keeps costs fair, delivers secure platforms, and ensures usability from day one.\"\n    },\n    \"section5\": {\n      \"title\": \"How We Work\",\n      \"steps\": [\n        {\n          \"step\": 1,\n          \"title\": \"Discovery & Planning\",\n          \"description\": \"We begin by understanding your audience, workflows, and long-term goals. As a web application development company in the USA, we design strategies for scalability and adoption.\",\n          \"margin\": \"0px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 2,\n          \"title\": \"Custom Design & Development\",\n      