(22, 'web-application-design', 'ui-ux-design', '{\n    \"title\": \"Web Application Design\",\n    \"section2\": {\n      \"title\": \"Wireframing & Prototyping Services\",\n      \"des\": \"Bringing an idea to life without a clear blueprint is risky. That’s why wireframing and prototyping services are essential for every business planning to launch a digital product. At Allspark Technologies, we transform your concepts into application wireframes and functional prototypes that make your vision tangible before development begins. Many businesses fear that the final app or website may not align with their expectations. Our structured wireframing solutions eliminate that risk by showing you exactly how the product will look, flow, and function, well before a single line of code is written. We help enterprises, SaaS companies, and startups visualize user journeys, test usability, and validate ideas with UI wireframe design and interactive prototypes that save time, reduce costs, and increase product success rates.\"\n    },\n    \"section3\": {\n      \"title\": \"Our Wireframing and Prototyping Process\",\n      \"image\": \"img1.png\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Understanding User Needs First\",\n          \"description\": \"Every web application wireframe begins with understanding your users. We map navigation flows, design usage scenarios, and identify pain points to ensure the final product delivers exceptional user experience.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Low-Fidelity Wireframes\",\n          \"description\": \"Instead of jumping straight into high-end design, we start with wireframe designs that highlight structure and layout. These cost-effective app design wireframes allow businesses to visualize functionality early and avoid expensive redesigns later.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Clickable Prototypes\",\n          \"description\": \"We create prototype wireframes and functional mockups to demonstrate real interactions. Clients can test navigation flows, review usability, and provide input while changes are still simple and affordable.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Iterative Feedback Loops\",\n          \"description\": \"Our wireframing UX design process involves continuous feedback. At every stage, you’ll see updates, share suggestions, and stay confident that the product is on track to meet business goals.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section4\": {\n      \"title\": \"Design Direction That Saves Time\",\n      \"des\": \"Wireframing and prototyping are the blueprints of digital product design. They bridge the gap between ideas and development by providing clarity, direction, and validation. Skipping wireframing can lead to misaligned expectations, wasted budgets, and frustrated users. With Allspark’s user experience design wireframes and functional application prototyping service, you gain peace of mind knowing your app or web product is built on a strong foundation.\"\n    },\n    \"section5\": {\n      \"title\": \"How We Work\",\n      \"steps\": [\n        {\n          \"step\": 1,\n          \"title\": \"Wireframing for Web & Mobile\",\n          \"description\": \"Clear layouts that define structure, navigation, and user flow.\",\n          \"margin\": \"0px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 2,\n          \"title\": \"Clickable Prototypes\",\n          \"description\": \"Interactive mockups to validate functionality and usability.\",\n          \"margin\": \"100px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 3,\n          \"title\": \"Navigation Flow Mapping\",\n          \"description\": \"Logical user journeys for web and mobile applications.\",\n          \"margin\": \"200px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 4,\n          \"title\": \"Design Usage Scenarios & Testing\",\n          \"description\": \"Explore real wireframe product design cases and validate early.\",\n          \"margin\": \"300px\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section6\": {\n      \"image\": \"img2.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Extended Section\",\n      \"des\": \"A poorly planned digital product often results in frustrated users, wasted budgets, and project delays. Many companies jump into design and coding without testing ideas, leading to multiple redesigns and development inefficiencies.\",\n      \"des2\": \"At Allspark Technologies, we prevent these challenges with wireframing and prototyping services that bring clarity early. Whether it’s an app wireframe design, a web app wireframe, or a wireframe for application testing, our approach ensures your product is validated, refined, and user-friendly before launch. From landing page wireframe design for startups to application wireframes for enterprise SaaS platforms, our services ensure your product works the way users expect before development even begins.\"\n    },\n    \"section7\": {\n      \"quote\": \"The prototype Allspark built saved our project. By testing with real users, we avoided design errors and launched a product our customers actually love.\",\n      \"author\": \"CTO, SaaS Startup\"\n    },\n    \"section8\": {\n      \"image\": \"img3.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Why Choose Us\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Reduce Risk of Wrong Direction\",\n          \"description\": \"Our wireframing solutions give you a clear roadmap before development starts.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Save Time & Budget\",\n          \"description\": \"With app wireframing and prototypes, costly late-stage changes are avoided.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Industry-Backed Methods\",\n          \"description\": \"We apply UX design wireframe and user experience prototyping consultancy standards used by leading digital product design companies.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Trusted Outsourcing Partner\",\n          \"description\": \"Global enterprises choose Allspark for user experience outsourcing and outsourced UX design because we deliver predictable, high-quality results.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section9\": {\n      \"title\": \"Industries We Serve\",\n      \"para\": \"We have extensive experience providing web application design across industries such as:\",\n      \"industries\": [\n        \"SaaS Platforms & Digital Product Startups\",\n        \"Enterprise Web Applications\",\n        \"E-commerce & Retail Platforms\",\n        \"Healthcare & Fitness Apps\",\n        \"Finance & Fintech Applications\",\n        \"Education & Training Platforms\",\n        \"Rewards Program Apps & Customer Engagement Tools\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"faq\": {\n      \"title\": \"Frequently Asked Questions\",\n      \"faqs\": [\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-1\",\n          \"ques\": \"Why is wireframing important before designing apps or websites?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Wireframing creates a visual structure for your project. It ensures clarity, prevents scope creep, and reduces development risks. Skipping this step often leads to costly redesigns and poor user experience.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-2\",\n          \"ques\": \"How detailed are your prototypes?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Our prototypes range from simple wireframe pictures to fully interactive prototype wireframes that simulate navigation flows. This flexibility allows you to test functionality before development.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-3\",\n          \"ques\": \"Does wireframing increase project costs?\",\n          \"ans\": \"No. Wireframing and prototyping actually save costs by identifying issues early. Instead of expensive late-stage fixes, we use wireframe product design methods to validate ideas first.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-4\",\n          \"ques\": \"Can prototypes be tested with real users?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Yes. Our functional application prototyping services allow usability testing on real scenarios. This ensures the final product meets user needs before going live.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-5\",\n          \"ques\": \"Do you support outsourced UX design projects?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Absolutely. Many companies outsource UX design and rely on Allspark as their user experience prototyping consultancy. We provide dedicated support to agencies and enterprises that need expert UI/UX services without hiring in-house teams.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"contact\": {\n      \"title\": \"Don’t risk costly redesigns or failed product launches.\",\n      \"subTitle\": \"Partner with Allspark Technologies for wireframing and prototyping services.\"\n    }\n}'),
(23, 'design-systems', 'ui-ux-design', '{\n    \"title\": \"Design Systems\",\n    \"section2\": {\n      \"title\": \"Design Systems and Branding Services\",\n      \"des\": \"Your brand is more than just a logo. It is the foundation of how customers perceive your business across every digital and physical interaction. At Allspark Technologies, we provide professional design and branding services that help businesses establish a consistent identity, build trust, and create lasting customer loyalty. Companies often fear that their brand identity will look unprofessional, fail to connect with their audience, or become inconsistent across platforms. Our branding and creative services eliminate these concerns by developing complete brand systems that deliver clarity, recognition, and a unified visual experience.\"\n    },\n    \"section3\": {\n      \"title\": \"Our Approach to Branding and Design Systems\",\n      \"image\": \"img1.png\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Understanding Brand Identity\",\n          \"description\": \"Every successful brand begins with a clear identity. As a brand identity design company, we analyze your values, target audience, and industry positioning to create a foundation that guides all branding efforts.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Logo Design and Visual Identity\",\n          \"description\": \"Our custom logo design agency focuses on creating unique company logos that reflect your business goals and communicate trust. From modern graphic logo designs to corporate identity development, we provide tailored branding logo design services for startups, enterprises, and established brands.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Building Design Systems\",\n          \"description\": \"Design systems ensure consistency across your digital platforms. We build scalable systems that include typography, color palettes, UI elements, and design foundations. These systems allow you to maintain brand uniformity across websites, applications, and marketing channels.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Prototyping and Visual Testing\",\n          \"description\": \"We provide visual mockups and branding prototypes that allow clients to see their design direction before implementation. This step reduces the risk of rework and ensures every element aligns with business goals.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Iterative Collaboration\",\n          \"description\": \"Our process is transparent and collaborative. You are involved at every stage, from wireframe visualization to final creative branding solutions. With iterative feedback, your identity evolves with precision and confidence.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section4\": {\n      \"title\": \"Comprehensive Branding and Creative Services\",\n      \"des\": \"At Allspark Technologies, we provide end-to-end branding and design services tailored to businesses of all sizes. From professional company logo design and brand identity development to complete business branding solutions, our team ensures your brand communicates trust and creativity. We deliver graphic design and branding services, corporate identity support, and digital design for web, mobile, and social platforms. Whether you’re a startup, SaaS provider, or enterprise, our visual identity design systems help establish a consistent, memorable, and impactful brand presence.\"\n    },\n    \"section5\": {\n      \"title\": \"How We Work\",\n      \"steps\": [\n        {\n          \"step\": 1,\n          \"title\": \"Discovery & Research\",\n          \"description\": \"We start by learning about your business, market, and audience to shape a strong brand strategy.\",\n          \"margin\": \"0px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 2,\n          \"title\": \"Strategy & Concept\",\n          \"description\": \"Our team defines brand identity elements like logo, colors, and voice for clear direction.\",\n          \"margin\": \"100px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 3,\n          \"title\": \"Logo & Identity Design\",\n          \"description\": \"We create unique, scalable logos and branding assets tailored to your business goals.\",\n          \"margin\": \"200px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 4,\n          \"title\": \"Design Systems\",\n          \"description\": \"We build brand guidelines and design systems to keep visuals consistent everywhere.\",\n          \"margin\": \"300px\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section6\": {\n      \"image\": \"img2.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Why Strong Branding Matters\",\n      \"des\": \"Design systems and branding are the backbone of digital presence. Without a structured approach, businesses risk weak brand recognition, inconsistent communication, and poor user experiences.\",\n      \"des2\": \"Allspark Technologies provides complete identity design services that help organizations stand out in competitive markets. Whether you are looking for the best logo design service, a full-service branding company, or digital designers near you, we ensure your brand communicates value and credibility. Building a strong brand identity goes beyond just a logo. At Allspark Technologies, our branding and creative services ensure your business stands out with a consistent visual identity, powerful messaging, and design systems that scale. From company logo design services to complete business branding solutions, we deliver strategies that connect with your audience and strengthen long-term growth.\"\n    },\n    \"section7\": {\n      \"quote\": \"Allspark Technologies transformed our vision into a professional brand identity. Their logo design and branding services gave us a consistent look across our website, app, and marketing. We now feel confident presenting our brand to clients worldwide.\",\n      \"author\": \"Sarah Mitchell, Founder of BrightPath C…\"\n    },\n    \"section8\": {\n      \"image\": \"img3.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Why Choose Allspark Technologies\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Proven Expertise\",\n          \"description\": \"Our team delivers professional branding and creative services trusted by businesses across industries.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"End-to-End Branding Solutions\",\n          \"description\": \"From logo design and branding to digital design systems, we manage the entire process seamlessly.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Experience Across Industries\",\n          \"description\": \"We provide scalable business branding services tailored to startups, SaaS platforms, and large enterprises.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Transparent Process\",\n          \"description\": \"Our branding design services prioritize open communication, keeping clients involved at every step.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Scalable Design Systems\",\n          \"description\": \"We create design and branding systems that ensure your company identity grows with your business.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Creative Strategies\",\n          \"description\": \"Every branding decision is rooted in research, ensuring stronger customer engagement and long-term brand value.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section9\": {\n      \"title\": \"Industries We Serve\",\n      \"para\": \"We have extensive experience providing design systems across industries such as:\",\n      \"industries\": [\n        \"Technology and Software Development Companies\",\n        \"E-commerce and Retail Brands\",\n        \"SaaS Businesses and Digital Startups\",\n        \"Healthcare and Wellness Organizations\",\n        \"Education and E-learning Platforms\",\n        \"Financial Services and Fintech Companies\",\n        \"Professional Services and Consulting Firms\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"faq\": {\n      \"title\": \"Frequently Asked Questions\",\n      \"faqs\": [\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-1\",\n          \"ques\": \"What is the difference between logo design and branding?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Logo design is the creation of a symbol or graphic that represents your business, while branding includes the full visual and emotional identity of your company. Our branding and graphic design services cover both aspects to ensure your business communicates consistently across all channels.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-2\",\n          \"ques\": \"Why do businesses need design systems?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Design systems provide a unified structure for colors, typography, and user interface components. They prevent inconsistencies across digital platforms and save time during design and development. As a brand identity company, we specialize in building scalable systems for long-term brand success.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-3\",\n          \"ques\": \"How do I know if my brand identity needs improvement?\",\n          \"ans\": \"If your audience finds your brand unrecognizable, if your designs vary across platforms, or if your logo no longer reflects your business direction, it is time to update your identity. Our branding and creative services help businesses refresh outdated visuals and align them with modern market expectations.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-4\",\n          \"ques\": \"Do you provide custom logo design agency services for startups?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Yes. We create business branding solutions for startups that need affordable yet professional identity design. From simple business logos to complete design and branding services, we ensure new companies start strong with a professional presence.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-5\",\n          \"ques\": \"Can you redesign my existing brand identity?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Absolutely. As a corporate identity design agency, we offer rebranding services that update logos, refine color palettes, and restructure brand systems while maintaining recognition.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-6\",\n          \"ques\": \"How do branding services impact marketing and customer trust?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Strong branding ensures consistency across marketing campaigns, digital platforms, and customer interactions. A clear visual identity improves recognition, builds trust, and increases engagement. Our branding logo design services integrate directly with marketing strategies to strengthen long-term business growth.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-7\",\n          \"ques\": \"What makes Allspark Technologies different from other branding companies?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Unlike many branding design studios, we combine creative design with technology expertise. As a digital-first brand identity design firm, we focus on scalable systems, usability, and cross-platform consistency that extend beyond just visuals.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"contact\": {\n      \"title\": \"Elevate your brand with Allspark Technologies.\",\n      \"subTitle\": \"From professional logo design services to complete design and branding systems.\"\n    }\n}'),
(24, 'usability-testing', 'ui-ux-design', '{\n    \"title\": \"Usability Testing\",\n    \"section2\": {\n      \"title\": \"Usability Testing & UX Audits\",\n      \"des\": \"A strong digital product depends on how easily people can use it. At Allspark Technologies, our usability testing and UX audit services uncover hidden issues, improve engagement, and reduce wasted development costs. From mobile apps to enterprise SaaS and online stores, our team delivers clear insights backed by a proven UX audit checklist so you can launch with confidence.\"\n    },\n    \"section3\": {\n      \"title\": \"Our Approach to Usability Testing and UX Audits\",\n      \"image\": \"img1.png\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Easy-to-Understand Audit Reports\",\n          \"description\": \"Every UX audit report is designed for both executives and developers. We avoid jargon and present findings with clear explanations, visuals, and UX audit samples so teams can act with confidence.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Cost-Effective Problem Solving\",\n          \"description\": \"Our UX audit services identify usability issues early, preventing expensive fixes later. By investing in proactive research, businesses save significant costs while improving user satisfaction.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Fast and Efficient Process\",\n          \"description\": \"We integrate usability testing and UX audits directly into your product development cycle. This efficiency ensures no delays, whether it’s a website UX audit agency project or a mobile app usability review.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Tailored to Industry Needs\",\n          \"description\": \"From UX audit pharma solutions to online store audits and SaaS platform evaluations, our services adapt to your industry. Every recommendation aligns with your unique business goals and compliance needs.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Actionable and Business-Focused Insights\",\n          \"description\": \"Instead of generic advice, our audits deliver step-by-step recommendations and a user experience audit checklist. This ensures improvements are practical, measurable, and directly tied to growth.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section4\": {\n      \"title\": \"Comprehensive Usability Testing and Audit Services\",\n      \"des\": \"Our UI UX audit services go beyond surface-level checks by blending real user testing, heuristic reviews, analytics, and accessibility standards into a single, actionable framework. As a trusted UX audit company, Allspark delivers a detailed user experience audit checklist tailored to your product. Each audit includes evaluations based on usability best practices, accessibility and compliance reviews, and conversion-focused testing for both websites and apps. We also specialize in UX audits for online stores to optimize sales funnels and conduct performance analysis across devices and browsers, ensuring your digital product delivers consistent, measurable results.\"\n    },\n    \"section5\": {\n      \"title\": \"Specialized Usability Testing & UX Audit Solutions\",\n      \"steps\": [\n        {\n          \"step\": 1,\n          \"title\": \"Discovery & Audit Planning\",\n          \"description\": \"We begin by understanding your product goals, user challenges, and industry requirements. Our website UX audit agency team creates a tailored plan using a proven user experience audit checklist.\",\n          \"margin\": \"0px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 2,\n          \"title\": \"Usability Testing & Research\",\n          \"description\": \"Next, we conduct mobile app usability testing, remote user studies, and accessibility compliance audits. This ensures both real users and business standards are considered from the start.\",\n          \"margin\": \"100px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 3,\n          \"title\": \"UX Audit Report & Recommendations\",\n          \"description\": \"We deliver detailed UX audit sample reports that include visuals, data insights, and actionable recommendations. Stakeholders gain clarity and confidence with step-by-step guidance.\",\n          \"margin\": \"200px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 4,\n          \"title\": \"Implementation Support & Validation\",\n          \"description\": \"Our team supports enterprise SaaS UX audit services, UI interaction flow validation, and agency audit UX solutions for global businesses. We ensure improvements are practical, scalable, and measurable.\",\n          \"margin\": \"300px\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section6\": {\n      \"image\": \"img2.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Clarity and Confidence for Every Digital Product\",\n      \"des\": \"A user experience audit is more than just a document, it is a strategic roadmap for measurable business growth. At Allspark Technologies, our UX audit services help identify hidden usability issues, streamline customer journeys, and uncover conversion opportunities. Whether you are a SaaS platform, a pharma company, or an online retail store, our UI UX audit services provide clarity by combining data-driven insights with practical solutions. Every recommendation is backed by real user research and a comprehensive user experience audit checklist, ensuring your investment drives tangible results.\",\n      \"des2\": \"One of the biggest concerns businesses have is wasting money on research that doesn’t deliver value. Our role as a trusted UX audit agency is to eliminate that fear by producing actionable, measurable outcomes. Each UX audit report includes prioritized improvements, usability testing findings, and scalable design recommendations. By tailoring our UX audit service to your business model, we make sure every decision directly impacts customer satisfaction and long-term product growth. Complexity is another challenge that prevents teams from taking action. That’s why our UX audit company goes beyond text-heavy documents. We provide clear visuals, UX audit samples, and step-by-step recommendations so your design and development teams can act quickly. Whether it’s optimizing workflows, refining a website UX audit agency deliverable, or scaling enterprise design systems, our process builds confidence while saving time. With Allspark’s comprehensive UX audit services, you gain a roadmap that empowers your team to make confident, data-backed improvements.\"\n    },\n    \"section7\": {\n      \"quote\": \"Partnering with Allspark for a UX audit transformed our customer portal. Their audit report was clear, actionable, and boosted task completion rates by 40% within weeks.\",\n      \"author\": \"David L., Senior Digital Marketer, SaaS\"\n    },\n    \"section8\": {\n      \"image\": \"img3.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Why Choose Allspark\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Proven Expertise\",\n          \"description\": \"We bring years of experience delivering UX audit services across industries, ensuring every project is backed by research-driven insights and practical solutions.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"End-to-End UI UX Audit Services\",\n          \"description\": \"From usability testing to detailed UX audit reports, our UI UX audit services cover every stage, tailored to your business goals and customer needs.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Specialized Solutions\",\n          \"description\": \"As a trusted UX audit company, we provide targeted audits for SaaS products, pharma solutions, and online retail stores, addressing sector-specific challenges.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Transparent Process\",\n          \"description\": \"Our UX audit checklist and UX audit samples make it easy to see where improvements are needed, helping teams act quickly and confidently.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Scalable Design Systems\",\n          \"description\": \"Beyond individual fixes, our UX audits include scalable recommendations and design systems that maintain consistency as your product grows.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Creative Strategies\",\n          \"description\": \"We combine proven usability testing methods with innovative UX audit strategies, ensuring every solution improves user experience and business performance.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section9\": {\n      \"title\": \"Industries We Serve\",\n      \"para\": \"We have extensive experience providing usability testing across industries such as:\",\n      \"industries\": [\n        \"E-commerce and Online Retail Stores\",\n        \"Healthcare and Pharma Platforms\",\n        \"Fintech, Banking, and Digital Wallets\",\n        \"SaaS and Enterprise Business Applications\",\n        \"Education and E-learning Platforms\",\n        \"Travel, Hospitality, and Booking Systems\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"faq\": {\n      \"title\": \"Frequently Asked Questions\",\n      \"faqs\": [\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-1\",\n          \"ques\": \"What is a UX audit service?\",\n          \"ans\": \"A UX audit service evaluates how users interact with your product. Using a UX audit checklist, our team identifies usability issues, accessibility gaps, and conversion barriers, then provides a clear UX audit report with recommendations.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-2\",\n          \"ques\": \"How does a UX audit save time and money?\",\n          \"ans\": \"By running an early user experience audit, businesses avoid costly redesigns. Fixing small usability issues uncovered by our UX audit services is faster and cheaper than rebuilding entire workflows later.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-3\",\n          \"ques\": \"Do you provide UX audits for live websites and mobile apps?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Yes. As a website UX audit agency and mobile UX audit company, we specialize in optimizing existing products. Live platforms benefit most from usability testing because real user data reveals friction points.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-4\",\n          \"ques\": \"Can you share a UX audit sample or checklist before starting?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Absolutely. We provide a user experience audit checklist and UX audit sample report so clients know exactly what to expect.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-5\",\n          \"ques\": \"Is this only for large enterprises?\",\n          \"ans\": \"No. Startups, SaaS teams, and online retailers benefit from UI UX audit services. Our scalable approach works for businesses of all sizes.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-6\",\n          \"ques\": \"Do you work with global businesses?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Yes, as an international UX audit company and agency audit UX partner, we provide usability audits in English, Spanish (auditoría UX), and French (agence audit UX) contexts.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"contact\": {\n      \"title\": \"Build experiences your users trust.\",\n      \"subTitle\": \"Schedule your usability testing and UX audit with Allspark Technologies today.\"\n    }\n}');

